Diane Michelle https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Diane_Michelle 0 Diane Michelle is an American voice actress, famous for voicing Daisy Duck in several modern Disney projects (Daisy is currently voiced by Tress MacNeille in many projects) in The Spirit of Mickey, Mickey Mouse Works and Mickey's Once Upon a Christmas.
